1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,140
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:00:47,180 --> 00:00:48,740
=Episode 22=
=No Escape From Fate=

11
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:01,040
What is it?

12
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:02,760
Turn around.

13
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:09,680
Why are you here?

14
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,590
Because I miss you.

15
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:21,510
Take a look at this.

16
00:01:40,430 --> 00:01:43,640
These are the exhibition drafts\
my mom kept revising.

17
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,070
Where did you find them?

18
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:47,840
That's a secret.

19
00:01:53,590 --> 00:01:54,430
Ye Lang.

20
00:01:55,140 --> 00:01:56,200
I want to give you a gift.

21
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,000
Help you fulfill

22
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,200
your mom's final wish.

23
00:02:00,070 --> 00:02:00,910
Okay?

24
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:07,430
Niannian.

25
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,430
I'm so lucky to have you.

26
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:27,120
This is the key to my mom's art gallery.

27
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,400
All the paintings

28
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,710
are kept in the basement.

29
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:32,960
I want us to do

30
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,520
this exhibition together.

31
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:38,960
Niannian,

32
00:02:39,630 --> 00:02:40,470
you know what?

33
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:43,240
Father agreed to let us marry.

34
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:47,560
We won't repeat my parents' path.

35
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,680
I'll break the curse,

36
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,120
and give you a steady,

37
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,080
happy future.

38
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,430
Once you take over the Li family,

39
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,800
what should I call you then?

40
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,870
Young Master?

41
00:03:18,310 --> 00:03:19,150
Or Mr. Ye?

42
00:03:22,910 --> 00:03:24,310
When I'm with you,

43
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,560
I'll always just be Ye Lang.

44
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:57,260
(Heart, Fresh Donor, O RH-Negative)

45
00:04:57,260 --> 00:04:58,380
(Organ Trafficking)

46
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,240
Why is there a dark web mark too?

47
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:07,910
Young Master.

48
00:05:09,070 --> 00:05:11,480
Replace all champagne with white wine.

49
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:13,230
Understood.

50
00:05:13,370 --> 00:05:14,230
Young Master,

51
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,630
the mayor and the major families

52
00:05:15,630 --> 00:05:16,560
are on their way.

53
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,040
- Three more...
- I want

54
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,480
no commercial deals for this exhibition.

55
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,760
But...

56
00:05:21,870 --> 00:05:23,020
This exhibition cannot go on.

57
00:05:28,390 --> 00:05:29,230
Niannian.

58
00:05:30,550 --> 00:05:31,420
Li Hong's dark web

59
00:05:31,430 --> 00:05:32,310
is just a smokescreen.

60
00:05:33,070 --> 00:05:34,800
The real dark web has been operating

61
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,120
for over a decade.

62
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,160
Its founder was

63
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,080
Ye Mei.

64
00:05:44,950 --> 00:05:46,750
This string of numbers is the website's IP.

65
00:05:47,270 --> 00:05:48,160
Behind it

66
00:05:48,310 --> 00:05:49,510
is an art auction platform.

67
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,320
Look closely.

68
00:05:58,070 --> 00:06:01,560
What's labeled beneath
these rare collectibles

69
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,720
isn't preservation data,

70
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,000
but blood types,

71
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,440
ages,

72
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:08,040
and health ratings.

73
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,440
That's impossible!

74
00:06:15,630 --> 00:06:16,470
Impossible.

75
00:06:17,510 --> 00:06:18,630
It can't be.

76
00:06:18,940 --> 00:06:19,800
My mom wouldn't do...

77
00:06:19,810 --> 00:06:21,430
You don't really know your mom.

78
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,440
Ye Lang.

79
00:06:23,950 --> 00:06:25,560
I've exposed all of this to the media.

80
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:28,510
I don't want more victims like Xiaodi.

81
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:33,080
Niannian!

82
00:06:49,390 --> 00:06:50,230
Mom,

83
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,920
three of the Li family are dead.

84
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:56,070
Today, I'll offer three sticks of incense.

85
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,070
For revenge,

86
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,270
I never erected a gravestone.

87
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,270
I've failed you.

88
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:10,800
In the previous life,

89
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:14,390
I failed because of Jiang Niannian.

90
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:16,600
But fate has

91
00:07:16,830 --> 00:07:18,720
given me another chance.

92
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,160
In this life,

93
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,600
I'll use Jiang Niannian

94
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,270
to drag the entire Li family

95
00:07:27,950 --> 00:07:29,120
down with you!

96
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:43,120
Li Hong may not be as healthy as you.

97
00:07:45,390 --> 00:07:46,360
But he

98
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:51,240
didn't need a heart transplant.

99
00:07:52,630 --> 00:07:53,800
His life

100
00:07:55,310 --> 00:07:57,040
was ruined by two lies.

101
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,560
Let me remind you.

102
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,510
Li Hong's attending physician,

103
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:05,630
the lead developer of God No.6

104
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:08,920
is Vice President

105
00:08:09,310 --> 00:08:10,150
Murong Xue.

106
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:11,910
(Just as I thought,)

107
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:13,680
(Murong Xue is like me,)

108
00:08:14,190 --> 00:08:15,800
(reborn with memories.)

109
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,560
Ye Lang,

110
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,390
rumors are spreading wildly.

111
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:23,880
This time,

112
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,920
is there really no way for you?

113
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,240
So you have to help me.

114
00:08:31,270 --> 00:08:32,150
Help me stop her.

115
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,200
She can't hurt anyone else.

116
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:36,390
What do you wanna do?

117
00:09:00,030 --> 00:09:01,120
At last,

118
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:04,550
my dream's coming true.

119
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,480
Is this how we end this time?

120
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:15,800
Ye Lang.

121
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:46,580
(CAUTION)

122
00:09:57,140 --> 00:09:58,860
(Ye Lang)

123
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:05,320
Sorry, the subscriber
you dialed is power off.

124
00:10:08,220 --> 00:10:09,940
(New message from Cloud Gallery)

125
00:10:14,900 --> 00:10:17,260
(Seeking O RH-Negative blood,
25, healthy heart)

126
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:21,620
(Completed)

127
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,200
Ye Lang, you maniac.

128
00:10:25,750 --> 00:10:27,360
You put your own heart on the dark web!

129
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:35,270
Sorry, the subscriber
you dialed is power off.

130
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,080
Using yourself as bait.

131
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:44,150
You really wanna die?

132
00:11:02,270 --> 00:11:03,630
Over a decade ago,

133
00:11:05,790 --> 00:11:07,360
my mother died in a

134
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:10,030
so-called medical accident.

135
00:11:11,390 --> 00:11:13,240
But she wasn't sick at all.

136
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,360
Her heart

137
00:11:17,750 --> 00:11:19,000
was taken

138
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:20,510
by your grandfather!

139
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,000
From then on,

140
00:11:30,550 --> 00:11:31,840
I swore

141
00:11:33,030 --> 00:11:35,080
I'd make every single one of you

142
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:36,630
pay with your lives!

143
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,200
You are

144
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,840
the second-to-last.

145
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:01,720
It turns out you planned it all.

146
00:12:02,630 --> 00:12:03,870
You're insane.

147
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,440
For your own selfish desires,

148
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:09,600
how many people have you killed?

149
00:12:11,030 --> 00:12:13,440
Those living people listed as "collections",

150
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:15,200
don't their lives matter?

151
00:12:17,510 --> 00:12:18,600
I knew Zheng Lu

152
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:20,510
wouldn't turn on you that easily.

153
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:25,270
You used yourself as bait.

154
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,240
Still as bold as ever.

155
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:31,480
Since you came here alone,

156
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:34,510
you should've known I had backup.

157
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,320
So what if I did?

158
00:12:38,270 --> 00:12:40,630
Anyone I want dead

159
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,910
has never escaped.

160
00:12:46,270 --> 00:12:47,360
Like...

161
00:12:51,150 --> 00:12:53,240
Ye Mei.

162
00:12:54,870 --> 00:12:56,240
So it was you who killed her.

163
00:12:57,270 --> 00:12:58,110
Why?

164
00:12:58,670 --> 00:12:59,550
Why?

165
00:12:59,870 --> 00:13:00,710
Why!

166
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:04,360
Because she found my fake identity,

167
00:13:05,150 --> 00:13:07,270
and my mother's death certificate.

168
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,510
So I deliberately

169
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:13,630
stoked Liu Yexi's jealousy.

170
00:13:14,270 --> 00:13:15,110
And

171
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:18,030
told Zhong Minghui
about her allergy medication.

172
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:21,390
I just watched her

173
00:13:22,790 --> 00:13:25,120
suffocate in agony.

174
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:30,000
Like my mother suffered in surgery.

175
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:40,630
Murong Xue!

176
00:13:41,720 --> 00:13:42,560
Open the door!

177
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,080
Murong Xue!

178
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,440
Murong Xue, open the door!

179
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,150
Murong Xue!

180
00:13:56,270 --> 00:13:57,510
How does it feel?

181
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:58,470
Ye Lang.

182
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:00,320
Now...

183
00:14:00,770 --> 00:14:01,630
Murong Xue!

184
00:14:01,630 --> 00:14:02,870
You're the one person

185
00:14:02,870 --> 00:14:05,030
who truly understands my pain!

186
00:14:05,550 --> 00:14:06,390
Open the door!

187
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:07,630
Murong Xue!

188
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:32,920
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

189
00:14:34,760 --> 00:14:40,960
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

190
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:48,520
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

191
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:51,720
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

192
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:56,720
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

193
00:14:56,720 --> 00:15:00,960
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

194
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:05,400
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

195
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:09,240
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

196
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:15,000
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

197
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:19,320
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

198
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:23,160
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

199
00:15:23,160 --> 00:15:27,680
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

200
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:32,520
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

201
00:15:32,920 --> 00:15:39,480
♪Life finds its way again♪
